column2: SELECT t.ra, t.dec, t.thingId, t.objID, p.rerun, p.run, p.camcol, p.field, p.mjd, p.score, p.psffwhm_u, p.psffwhm_g, p.psffwhm_r, p.psffwhm_i, p.psffwhm_z, p.nMgyPerCount_u, p.nMgyPerCount_g, p.nMgyPerCount_r, p.nMgyPerCount_i, p.nMgyPerCount_z, p.skyIvar_u, p.skyIvar_g, p.skyIvar_r, p.skyIvar_i, p.skyIvar_z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z, p.airmass_u, p.airmass_g, p.airmass_r, p.airmass_i, p.airmass_z, f.sky_u, f.sky_g, f.sky_r, f.sky_i, f.sky_z, f.skyErr_u, f.skyErr_g, f.skyErr_r, f.skyErr_i, f.skyErr_z, f.darkVariance_u, f.darkVariance_g, f.darkVariance_r, f.darkVariance_i, f.darkVariance_z, f.gain_u, f.gain_g, f.gain_r, f.gain_i, f.gain_z into mydb.phl2#b from thingIndex AS t JOIN detectionIndex AS d ON d.thingId = t.thingId JOIN photoObjAll as p on d.objId = p.objID JOIN Field as f on p.fieldid = f.fieldid WHERE t.objId = (SELECT po.objid FROM PhotoObj po, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) n WHERE n.objID = po.objID)
